      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical mechanical updates have been performed, including reinforced rear subframe mounting points and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the chassis handles the 333hp output with precision. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for optimized turn-in and lateral stability. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
